    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 116.</p><p>Unbreakable Stance</p><p>Channel, Durandal</p><p>Classes: Barbarian, Monk, Paladin Channeling Time: 1 action Base LP Cost: 0 LP Range: Self Duration: 1 round</p><p>You bolster yourself with unbreakable might, flowing from your soul to every last fiber of your body. You regain 1 Legendary Point and become resistant to all non-legendary damage except force, poison, and psychic until the start of your next turn. For the duration, your speed becomes 0 and you cannot be shoved or knocked prone against your will. You must be standing on solid ground to use this Mythical Technique.</p><p>LP Cost. You can expend 1 Legendary Point to instead become immune to all non-legendary damage and resistant to dark, force, lethal, poison, psychic and soul damage for the duration.</p></div>",
